30
00:2:32,600-->00:2:35,600
It's a bonsai tree 这是一颗盆栽for your new apartment. 祝贺 迁新居。

31
00:2:35,600-->00:2:38,600
Hi, Marilyn. I hope it's not too late. 好 Marilyn 我舷 望我来得不算太晚。

32
00:2:38,600-->00:2:40,600
Oh, not at all. We're still eating. 噢 没关 。我们还还在吃著呢

33
00:2:40,600-->00:2:43,600
Please, come in. Join us. 请进。跟我们一起吃吃吧

34
00:2:43,600-->00:2:45,600
