38
00:2:54,600-->00:2:58,600
Yes, I think it's important for me to be there 是的 我想我在场是是非常重要

39
00:2:58,600-->00:2:59,600
since her mother died. 因为她妈妈去世了。

40
00:2:59,600-->00:3:3,600
