57
00:3:42,600-->00:3:44,600
I like that. 我喜欢这样。

58
00:3:44,600-->00:3:57,600
And then, two years ago, my wife died. 接著 两年前我妻子子去世了

59
00:3:57,600-->00:3:59,600
You miss her. 你思念她。

60
00:3:59,600-->00:4:4,600
I do...yes, but I have Michelle... 不错……是的 但我我还有Michelle…

61
00:4:4,600-->00:4:6,600
