68
00:4:26,600-->00:4:27,600
and the baby-sitter has to get home. 而且临时保姆也该回回家了

69
00:4:27,600-->00:4:30,600
Where did the time go? 时间溜到那 去了

70
00:4:30,600-->00:4:32,600
